        "layout": "noBorders"
      },
      {
        "style": "annexure-content",
        "table": {
          "widths": [
            "*"
          ],
          "body": [
            [
              {
                "text": "Please see below for further information about the private complaint against you ({{cmpNumber}}). You can also find this information and related documents on {{courtUrl}} (hereinafter referred to as “Portal”).",
                "style": "annexure-content"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "text": "1. How to Access Your Case Information and Documents",
                "style": "annexure-sub-header"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "text": "Once you register on the portal, you can log in and join your case using this 6 digit code: {{accessCode}}. Do not share this code with anyone other than your lawyer. The complaint and related documents filed by the complainant are available on the complaint tab of the Portal.",
                "style": "annexure-content"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "text": "This notice is merely to give you an opportunity of being heard even before a case is admitted, to enable you to share your version of the events with the presiding judicial officer.",
                "style": "annexure-content"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "text": "2. What to do next if you wish to show cause to the court not to take cognisance of this case?",
                "style": "annexure-sub-header"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "ul": [
                  {
                    "text": [
                      {
                        "text": "Confirm your representation: ",
                        "color": "#000000",
                        "bold": true
                      },
                      {
                        "text": "You may hire a lawyer to represent yourself or appear as a party in person, which means you represent yourself in court proceedings. Please visit Kerala Bar Council website {{barCouncilUrl}} for a contact directory of lawyers.",
                        "style": "annexure-content"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": [
                      {
                        "text": "Join the Case: ",
                        "color": "#000000",
                        "bold": true
                      },
                      {
                        "text": "Log in to the Portal & enter the 6-digit code {{accessCode}} to access your case details. You can use your mobile number to register/login on the portal",
                        "style": "annexure-content"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": [
                      {
                        "text": "Request a different hearing date: ",
                        "color": "#000000",
                        "bold": true
                      },
                      {
                        "text": "If you cannot attend your hearing on {{hearingDate}}, you can request a new date through the Portal.",
                        "style": "annexure-content"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ],
                "style": "annexure-sub-content"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "text": "3. Options for Quicker Resolution of Your Case",
                "style": "annexure-sub-header"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "ul": [
                  {
                    "text": "You may choose to settle the dispute with the complainant. This can be a quicker and simpler way of resolution. For this, you may approach the complainant directly, or you may sign up for a Lok Adalat/Mediation Session that is overseen by the court. ",
                    "style": "annexure-text"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "If you choose to settle the dispute, you may inform the court after joining the case on the Portal on the intended day of hearing.",
                    "style": "annexure-text"
                  }
                ],
                "style": "annexure-sub-content"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "text": "Need Help?",
                "style": "annexure-sub-header"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "text": " If you have any questions or need help, please visit your nearest e-Sewa Kendra or contact {{courtContact}}",
                "style": "annexure-content"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "text": "Privacy notice:",
                "style": "annexure-sub-header"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "text": [
                  {
                    "text": "The court gets a notification when you open and login through the above links. This information is only accessible to the Judiciary in accordance with this ",
                    "style": "annexure-content"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "Privacy Policy",
                    "color": "#0000FF",
                    "decoration": "underline",
                    "style": "annexure-content"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": ".",
                    "style": "annexure-content"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          ]
